data.description: Country Living! Check out this three bedroom, three bath home located in Grover, North Carolina! With over 1900 square feet, this home comes with tons of space to make your own. When you drive onto the property, you will notice a ton of yard space. This home comes with over 1.50 acres of land perfect for folks who do not want to be on top of their neighbors. When you walk into the home, the first thing you will notice is the open concept. This makes this home perfect to entertain guests. Home features a split bedroom plan with two flex spaces that could be used as extra bedrooms or office spaces. Downtown Grover is a little over 5 minutes and Downtown Shelby is around a 15 minute drive putting this home in a great location. Do not miss your chance to own a piece of country heaven!
